COMPUTE x = id.
COMPUTE x2 = x * x.
EXECUTE.

* Statistik Deskriptif.
TEMPORARY.
SELECT IF (id <= 24).
DESCRIPTIVES VARIABLES = pelanggan kwh
  /STATISTICS = MEAN STDDEV MIN MAX.

TEMPORARY.
SELECT IF (id <= 24).
FREQUENCIES VARIABLES = pelanggan
  /STATISTICS = MEAN MEDIAN MODE MIN MAX STDDEV.

* Regresi Parabola -- semua var di VARIABLES kecuali dependen otomatis jadi prediktor.
* SAVE PRED bikin variabel PRED1.
REGRESSION
  /VARIABLES pelanggan x x2
  /DEPENDENT pelanggan
  /STATISTICS R ANOVA COEFF
  /SAVE PRED.

* Tampilkan hasil.
LIST id tahun pelanggan PRED1.
